data.description: Take a look at this recently updated move-in ready home featuring neutral colors that exude both warmth and style. The open concept living spaces are perfect for entertaining family and friends. With 3 nice sized bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, ample storage throughout, and a large yard, you will see why this home is the one for you! Come see this affordably priced gem that is conveniently located,  minutes from shopping, restaurants, grocery stores, BAFB, and schools.
